Scenario-Based Questions

9. How would you handle a stock mismatch issue between system and physical count?
→ Perform a cycle count, reconcile data, identify causes (data entry errors, theft, or damage), and adjust inventory records.


10. What happens when the same item exists in multiple warehouses?
→ Maintain location-wise stock using a Warehouse table and link it with product IDs.


11. If two users update stock at the same time, how do you prevent conflicts?
→ Use transactions and locking mechanisms in the database.

